Title: Do Her / Don't Do Her
Plot: In the Season 7 finale, Silas turns the tables on Nancy, as Shane makes one last attempt to keep her out of harm's way and the clutches of Detective Ouellette. Meanwhile, back on Wall Street, Doug schemes to keep his hedge-fund scam alive.
GuestStars: Madeline Walter, Ian Reed Kesler, Amad Jackson, Seth Isler, David Greenman
